          %div
            .left{:style => "width:50%"}
              %pre
                %code.html
                  :preserve
                    &lt;p>
                      Imagine there's no Heaven &lt;br/>
                      It's easy if you try &lt;br/>
                      No hell below us  &lt;br/>
                      Above us only sky
                    &lt;/p>
            .left.left-align{:style => "width:50%"}
              %p
                Imagine there's no Heaven
                %br/
                It's easy if you try
                %br/
                No hell below us
                %br/
                Above us only sky
            .clear
            %br/
            %br/
            %p * Notice: This tag does is our first example of a stand-alone or "self-closing" element. A break can't contain anything.
       
