                  Here is a paragraph with
                  %em Emphasized
                  text and
                  %strong Important
                  text.
              .clear
              %br/
              %br/
              %p * Notice: em and strong are meant to indicate meaning through style. If you want to have italicized for appearance and not to communicate meaning, you should use CSS.
          
